"\n"
"Je kan de gegevens van je bestelling bekijken op {url}\n"
"\n"
"Met vriendelijke groeten,\n"
"De organisatie van {event}"

#: base/configurations/default_setting.py:1887
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Hello,\n"
"\n"
"we approved your order for {event} and will be happy to welcome you\n"
"at our event.\n"
"\n"
"Please continue by paying for your order before {expire_date}.\n"
"\n"
"You can select a payment method and perform the payment here:\n"
"\n"
"{url}\n"
"\n"
"Best regards,\n"
"Your {event} team"
msgstr ""
"Hoi,\n"
"\n"
"We hebben je bestelling voor {event} goedgekeurd.\n"
"\n"
"Ga verder met je bestelling door te betalen voor {expire_date}.\n"
"\n"
"Je kan via de volgende link een betalingsmethode kiezen en betalen:\n"
"{url}\n"
"\n"
"Met vriendelijke groeten,\n"
"De organisatie van {event}"

#: base/configurations/default_setting.py:1907
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Hello,\n"
"\n"
"we approved your order for {event} and will be happy to welcome you\n"
"at our event. As you only ordered free products, no payment is required.\n"
"\n"
"You can change your order details and view the status of your order at\n"
"{url}\n"
